SCHEMA: fluid/leak_state.schema
schema_id: dominium.schema.fluid.leak_state
schema_version: 1.0.0
stability: core

PURPOSE:
- Canonical deterministic leak state emitted/consumed by FLUID containment processes.

REQUIRED SHAPE:
record leak_state
  required:
    - schema_version: semver
    - target_id: id
    - leak_rate: number
    - active: bool
    - last_update_tick: u64
    - deterministic_fingerprint: sha256
    - extensions: map